<h1>Ferni Design System</h1>
<p class="lead">
  A comprehensive design system for building human-centered AI experiences.
  Every token, component, and pattern is designed to make AI feel more human.
</p>

<section class="section">
  <h2>Philosophy</h2>
  <p>
    <strong>We believe in making AI human, and the decisions we make will reflect that.</strong>
  </p>
  <p>
    The Ferni Design System embodies this philosophy through warm colors, organic animations,
    and thoughtful interactions that create genuine connections between people and AI.
  </p>
</section>

<section class="section">
