<section class="section">
  <h2>Quick Start</h2>
  <p>Include the design tokens in your project:</p>

  <pre><code>&lt;!-- CSS Variables --&gt;
&lt;link rel="stylesheet" href="https://design.ferni.ai/tokens.css"&gt;

&lt;!-- Or import in your CSS --&gt;
@import url('https://design.ferni.ai/tokens.css');</code></pre>

  <p>Then use the CSS variables in your styles:</p>

  <pre><code>.my-component {
  background: var(--bg-elevated);
  color: var(--text-primary);
  border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
  padding: var(--space-4);
  transition: all var(--duration-normal) var(--ease-out);
}</code></pre>
</section>

